{"tid":1306511,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開+整合]為義士籌款義賣-香港加油Tee","createTime":"2019-07-11T07:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T20:07:24.000Z","uid":224817,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cb552e183afbf243ad7107669aa24ab2e437a2d5","tid":1306511,"uid":224817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"上post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299694\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299694</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGc6Zq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGc6Zq6.jpg&h=dfd6074a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我都係一路做一路學, 有不足之處有賴其他巴絲提點, 令我呢個project可以更完善, 多謝大家支持<br />\n<br />\n[最多人問:舊款既衫仲有冇得訂?]<br />\n<br />\n其實而家有文宣幫緊我出其他新款(好似係)<br />\n呢款截止後又會再推下一款<br />\n<br />\n直到推到差唔多 就會全部款再做<br />\n<br />\n而家以免我tg收order太混亂(其實已經好難快速覆哂大家, 請見諒)<br />\n暫時一次處理一個款先<br />\n<br />\n利申1: 發起人分文不收兼自付所有成本, 而發起人同所有相關組織無任何直接聯繫<br />\n<br />\n利申2: 已獲設計師授權採用<br />\n<br />\n原創: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheLovelyWorld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheLovelyWorld%2F&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8526ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=58d44509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheLovelyWorld/</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有意訂購朋友, 請於今日起HSBC櫃員機直接入數港幣$200或以上給予星火同盟 或其他支援抗爭者組織 (<span style=\"color: red;\">不需要付錢給製作方!!</span>)<br />\n<br />\nUpdate:<br />\n本身我係想大家睇到個post去捐既, 但係有d人不嬲有捐開, 所以我而家將個range定係7月內有捐錢都得, 只希望你地捐錢唔係一次性, 之後regular捐<br />\n<br />\n滙豐銀行: 048-857585-838 <br />\n戶口名稱: T PR**E M*L T*A T*C<br />\n<br />\n[點解揀星火?]<br />\n我點解揀星火個account放出黎 係因為我有次捐錢比佢地 佢地同我講 就算全部人唔記得哂班義士 星火都唔會放棄<br />\n當然其他組織我都歡迎, 最緊要幫到義士<br />\n<br />\n將收據tg傳給 @staytogetherhk 以確認訂購數量及尺寸 最好幾個朋友一齊訂<br />\n<br />\n同朋友一齊整合捐同交收, 係可以稍為保障到大家; 亦可以令唔同組織收多d捐款, 希望多多支持<br />\n<br />\n尺碼表:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J10XmD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ10XmD3.jpg&h=66ae2e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截止日期 15/7/2019<br />\n取貨日期 七月下旬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n取貨方式:<br />\n<br />\n1. 順豐到付;<br />\n可以用假名, 順豐站自提, 太空卡no.<br />\n千祈唔好比屋企地址我<br />\n2. 沙田/觀塘/屯門面交<br />\n據我所知而家買衫同賣衫都唔犯法既<br />\n3.商場儲物櫃<br />\n我可以放入去儲物櫃 tg個密碼比要拎貨既人<br />\n咁就可以唔見面 無痕拎貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勿忘義士 齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">提醒大家 d狗癲既 做左件衫自己珍藏或者著去發夢 千祈唔好平時著</span>"},{"pid":"aa3d7381664f9204081cd4b22ea76970b52bb46e","tid":1306511,"uid":224817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:31:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6a36f4b9a1904845ecf779b1f2ad3699b47ec2c4","tid":1306511,"uid":5524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"e5f4435097ab6af4f875e18163e37c4868e8d5d2","tid":1306511,"uid":224817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"ad71ead50e570a11c12501223152ad76ed1a1407","tid":1306511,"uid":224817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"cea63f0f25284995b4850ed4820922e69c037301","tid":1306511,"uid":224817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"我要投訴你"},{"pid":"905ee698e07aef1448318bed6a726f3452572645","tid":1306511,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8835ac8efc42fc2c0a90edc16ef99bd9dc782fe9","tid":1306511,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f508457829dbe26bf70b2250cffa9e59efe04950","tid":1306511,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1306511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t